randoop

Class RMethod

  • Object
    • RMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, StatementKind

    public final class RMethod
extends Object
implements StatementKind, Serializable
    Represents a method call. The "R" stands for "Randoop", to underline the distinction from java.lang.reflect.Method.
